data.description: Great ranch set back from the street on a lakefront lot in a popular neighborhood. Very close to public park with a splash pad, library and elementary school. 3 beds, 2 baths plus a bonus room. Almost everything is new...windows, frig, stove top, dish washer, roof, hot water heater, HVAC, hardwood floors, carpet and tiling in master bath.  Playset stays with the property.  Crawl space is stand up height.   Great room has a fireplace with a gas starter.  Neighborhood is close to schools, shopping, and churches.
